<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-10 offset-md-1" style="margin-top: 150px">
      <div class="card">
        <h5 class="card-header">Add New Employee</h5>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Please complete the following fields</h5>
          <form>
            <div class="form-row">

              <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                <label for="inputFirstName4">First Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputFirstName4" placeholder="First Name">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                <label for="inputLastName4">Last Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputLastName4" placeholder="Last Name">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">

              <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                <label for="inputBirthDate4">Birth Date</label>
                <input type="date" class="form-control" id="inputBirthDate4" placeholder="Birth Date">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                <label for="inputHireDate4">Hire Date</label>
                <input type="date" class="form-control" id="inputHireDate4" placeholder="Hire Date">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="inputGender4">Gender</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputGender4" placeholder="M/F">
              </div>

              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="inputEmail4">Email</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="inputEmail4" placeholder="Email">
              </div>

              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="inputEducation">Education</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputEducation"
                  placeholder="Degree Level and Concentration">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="inputSalary">Salary</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputSalary" placeholder="Salary">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="category">Department</label>
                <select class="custom-select" id="department">
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="category">Project</label>
                <select class="custom-select" id="project">
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="category">Title</label>
                <select class="custom-select" id="title">
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="category">Position</label>
                <select class="custom-select" id="position">
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="my-3"><strong>About You</strong></h3>
            <hr>

            <h3 class="q-space"><strong>Question 1</strong></h3>
            <h4 class="s-space">Do you feel being engaged in the community will help you better in accomplishing your professional goals?</h4>
            <select class="chosen-select" id="q1">
              <option value=""></option>
              <option value="1">1 (Strongly Disagree)</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3">3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5 (Strongly Agree)</option>
            </select>

            <h3 class="q-space"><strong>Question 2</strong></h3>
            <h4 class="s-space">You identify yourself as more of a technical person rather than a management person.</h4>
            <select class="chosen-select" id="q2">
              <option value=""></option>
              <option value="1">1 (Strongly Disagree)</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3">3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5 (Strongly Agree)</option>
            </select>


            <h3 class="q-space"><strong>Question 3</strong></h3>
            <h4 class="s-space">Public Speaking and Leadership Skills are of vital importance to you.</h4>
            <select class="chosen-select" id="q3">
              <option value=""></option>
              <option value="1">1 (Strongly Disagree)</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3">3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5 (Strongly Agree)</option>
            </select>

            <h3 class="q-space"><strong>Question 4</strong></h3>
            <h4 class="s-space"> Self-growth by higher education, professional certifications, workshops is your way of working towards your goals.</h4>
            <select class="chosen-select" id="q4">
              <option value=""></option>
              <option value="1">1 (Strongly Disagree)</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3">3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5 (Strongly Agree)</option>
            </select>

            <h3 class="q-space"><strong>Question 5</strong></h3>
            <h4 class="s-space">Apart from professional goals, personal goals such as new hobbies, new crafts excite you.</h4>
            <select class="chosen-select" id="q5">
              <option value=""></option>
              <option value="1">1 (Strongly Disagree)</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3">3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5 (Strongly Agree)</option>
            </select>

            <button id="submit" class=" my-5 btn btn-lg btn-block btn-primary">Submit</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
